[73] [CITE[SMIL 3.0 DAISY Profile]] ([TIME[2008-12-02 00:45:09 +09:00]] 版) <http://www.w3.org/TR/2008/REC-SMIL3-20081201/smil-daisy-profile.html#DaisyProfileNS-XhtmlRole>@


